				The Sneaking behind effect works for getting quests too (unless the guy your talking to actively wanted to lop your head off with his big sword, duh)- it basically removes all faction while you do it. Just remember to keep going round the back of people while you talk to them cos they turn round to face you when you speak. Also if you have to give them anything do it while sneaking behind too or you get nothing for it. Do this enough and soon everyone will be your bestest buddy, even for a DE. :P<BR>
